if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_purchase')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_purchase
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_purchase */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_purchase (
PurchaseID int identity,
Code nvarchar(50) null,
Count int null,
SupplierID int null,
PurchaseType int null,
IsLock bit null,
MOrderCode nvarchar(50) null,
Fee decimal(10,2) null,
Money decimal(10,2) null,
Remark nvarchar(500) null,
getRemark nvarchar(500 null,
IsHandle int null,
HandleRemark nvarchar(500) null,
PurchaseAdmin int null,
LockAdmin int null,
Status int null,
MMailCode nvarchar(20) null,
ImportTime datetime null,
PurchaseTime datetime null,
CheckTime datetime null,
AppTime datetime null,
SendTime datetime null,
constraint PK_BUSI_PURCHASE primary key (PurchaseID)
)
go
